==Current Cabinet==
{{main|United Indonesia Cabinet}}
The present Indonesian cabinet is the United Indonesia Cabinet, which was announced on 20 October 2004<ref name="JAKPOS211004">''The Jakarta Post'' 21 October 2004</ref>.

